Google has promoted their products in various ways. In [[London]], [http://www.google.co.uk/googlespace/ Google Space] was set-up in [[Heathrow Airport]], which showcased several of their products, including Gmail, Google Earth and Picasa. Also, a similar page was launched for American college students, under the name "[http://services.google.com/university/ College life, powered by Google]". This summarised the products that would be useful to people during education.
